128typedef struct {
129 int32_t *pSrcA; // pointer to the first vector
130 int32_t *pSrcB; // pointer to the second vector
131 uint32_t blkSizePE; // number of samples in each vector
132 uint32_t nPE; // number of processing units
133 int32_t *resBuffer; // pointer to result vector
134} plp_dot_prod_instance_i32;

151} plp_dot_prod_instance_q32;
